name: Kekcoin (ETH)
description: Kekcoin ($KEK) is a cryptocurrency project that distinguishes itself as more than just a fleeting memecoin. It aims to honor and embody the essence of internet humor and meme culture. Unlike the numerous Inu-themed coins in the cryptocurrency scene, KEKcoin is designed to celebrate meme lords and the origins of internet humor.
